body_html: I think you can try (1) benchmark transpose alone with size = 20 and size = 21; and (2) turn on/off optimizations individually to see which optimization is related (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.3/tensorflow/core/protobuf/config.proto#L85). I know constant folding won't be applied if the size of the constant in bytes is too large (> 10M) to prevents the size of the Graph from growing too large. But I don't see how it could be related to transpose, which I don't think could be folded anyway.
